<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:05:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>解释者：美国制裁的以色列定居者是谁？他们的目标意味着什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/who-are-the-israeli-settlers-sanctioned-by-the-u-s-and-what-does-their-targeting-mean/0000018d-8233-d636-adef-ceffc2980000</link><description>以色列银行开始封锁犹太定居者的账户，以遵守拜登政府因袭击巴勒斯坦人而对四名以色列定居者实施的制裁。他们是谁？对未来可能产生哪些影响？</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 13:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/who-are-the-israeli-settlers-sanctioned-by-the-u-s-and-what-does-their-targeting-mean/0000018d-8233-d636-adef-ceffc2980000</guid></item><item><title>人质仍然是辛瓦尔最有效的杠杆，也是他在谈判中唯一讨价还价的筹码</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-remain-sinwars-most-effective-lever-and-his-only-bargaining-chip-in-talks/0000018d-82b0-d6dc-ab9f-cffdfb5b0000</link><description>哈马斯在加沙和国外的领导层非常清楚，只有人质问题才能让数以万计的以色列人走上街头，也只有这场斗争才能迫使内塔尼亚胡处理棘手的问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 13:07:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-remain-sinwars-most-effective-lever-and-his-only-bargaining-chip-in-talks/0000018d-82b0-d6dc-ab9f-cffdfb5b0000</guid></item><item><title>心理学家阻止下一个摩萨德叛徒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-psychologists-stopping-the-next-mossad-traitor/0000018d-7f37-daa1-a9fd-7f3ff0e80000</link><description>以色列情报部门不仅使用心理分析来分析敌人，还用于筛查和治疗在敌对领土上进行作战活动的人员，因为他们知道他们冒着生命危险</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:58:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-psychologists-stopping-the-next-mossad-traitor/0000018d-7f37-daa1-a9fd-7f3ff0e80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的暴雨揭示了古老的亚述圣甲虫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-07/ty-article/rainstorm-in-israel-reveals-ancient-assyrian-scarab/0000018d-8358-dfd5-adff-dbf9f16b0000</link><description>圣甲虫印章是用半宝石红玉髓雕刻而成，一侧似乎显示出一只狮鹫，或者可能是一只有翼的四足动物。确定圣甲虫的年代很有挑战性，但它看起来最像公元前八世纪的圣甲虫</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:02:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-07/ty-article/rainstorm-in-israel-reveals-ancient-assyrian-scarab/0000018d-8358-dfd5-adff-dbf9f16b0000</guid></item><item><title>“他是犹太人？不，他只是爱以色列”：阿根廷总统在西墙受到英雄般的欢迎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-just-loves-israel-argentine-president-milei-gets-heros-welcome-at-western-wall/0000018d-830e-d636-adef-cfee20ee0000</link><description>周二，极右翼阿根廷领导人哈维尔·米莱（Javier Milei），又名“大头发的家伙”，在他为期三天的以色列之行的第一站吸引了喧闹的人群。一位以色列人解释说，“我们需要更多像他这样的人——全世界都在反对我们”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 10:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-just-loves-israel-argentine-president-milei-gets-heros-welcome-at-western-wall/0000018d-830e-d636-adef-cfee20ee0000</guid></item><item><title>“难以忍受的过度拥挤”：哈马斯战争期间以色列设施中的囚犯被关在拥挤的牢房里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/intolerable-overcrowding-prisoners-held-in-packed-cells-in-israel-amid-hamas-war/0000018d-8231-d6dc-ab9f-cf7de6820000</link><description>根据公设辩护人办公室的一份报告，囚犯遭受“卫生条件差、卫生问题和虫害困扰”，大约 3,400 名囚犯睡在地板上的床垫上</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 10:38:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/intolerable-overcrowding-prisoners-held-in-packed-cells-in-israel-amid-hamas-war/0000018d-8231-d6dc-ab9f-cf7de6820000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯提议停火135天、以色列从加沙撤军、谈判结束战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/hamas-proposes-135-day-cease-fire-israeli-withdrawal-from-gaza-talks-to-end-war/0000018d-82b3-d6dc-ab9f-cfffb16f0000</link><description>根据三阶段停火草案，将用人质换取1500名巴勒斯坦囚犯，移交被杀人质的遗体，以军全面撤军</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 10:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/hamas-proposes-135-day-cease-fire-israeli-withdrawal-from-gaza-talks-to-end-war/0000018d-82b3-d6dc-ab9f-cfffb16f0000</guid></item><item><title>沙特阿拉伯排除在没有巴勒斯坦国的情况下与以色列建立联系，结束加沙“侵略”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-rules-out-diplomatic-ties-with-israel-without-independent-palestinian-state/0000018d-829e-d636-adef-cefefe590000</link><description>就在美国国家安全委员会发言人约翰·柯比表示释放人质和以色列与沙特关系正常化问题是“不同的轨道”的一天后，沙特阿拉伯外交部表示，如果没有巴勒斯坦国，就不会有任何关系</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:37:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-rules-out-diplomatic-ties-with-israel-without-independent-palestinian-state/0000018d-829e-d636-adef-cefefe590000</guid></item><item><title>在史前波兰发现的青铜珠宝可能是祭祀品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-07/ty-article/bronze-jewels-found-in-prehistoric-poland-may-have-been-ritual-sacrifices/0000018d-7eda-d6dc-ab9f-7fffac880000</link><description>人们认为欧洲青铜时代的海乌姆诺文化不使用金属。但新的研究认为，古代湖床上的青铜首饰可能是代替人类提供的</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-07/ty-article/bronze-jewels-found-in-prehistoric-poland-may-have-been-ritual-sacrifices/0000018d-7eda-d6dc-ab9f-7fffac880000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部城市卡夫卡塞姆的一名男子在家中被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-his-home-in-central-israeli-city-of-kafr-qasem/0000018d-8230-d6dc-ab9f-cf7de0bc0000</link><description>以色列阿拉伯社区凶杀率急剧上升，48 岁男子在家中被谋杀</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:17:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-his-home-in-central-israeli-city-of-kafr-qasem/0000018d-8230-d6dc-ab9f-cf7de0bc0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡为了空洞的口号和政治利益牺牲了加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sacrificed-the-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-for-empty-slogans-and-political-gain/0000018d-8047-d636-adef-ceef8b310000</link><description>《纽约时报》有关仍被哈马斯俘虏的以色列人命运的报道对于政界或军事界的任何人来说都不足为奇。家人声称“时间不多了”的说法如今听起来截然不同</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:02:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sacrificed-the-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-for-empty-slogans-and-political-gain/0000018d-8047-d636-adef-ceef8b310000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡拒绝调解努力，人质家属加大力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-to-intensify-their-campaign-as-netanyahu-rebuffs-mediation-efforts/0000018d-8003-daa1-a9fd-e20baf6b0000</link><description>哈马斯再次要求结束战争作为达成任何协议的条件，而内塔尼亚胡部分出于政治原因表示反对。即使达成临时协议似乎也还有很长的路要走 ■ 有报道称，在囚禁期间死亡的人质人数比以色列承认的还要多，政府似乎对战争失去了兴趣</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:01:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-to-intensify-their-campaign-as-netanyahu-rebuffs-mediation-efforts/0000018d-8003-daa1-a9fd-e20baf6b0000</guid></item><item><title>埃及消息人士称，新一轮人质谈判将于周四在开罗开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-live/israel-reviewing-hamas-response-to-hostage-proposal-idf-officer-killed-in-gaza/0000018d-8196-d6dc-ab9f-cfff8a840000</link><description>据路透社报道，哈马斯在停火提案中寻求交换囚犯、交换人质以及撤出以色列军队。加沙真菌感染已导致死亡 ■《纽约时报》报道：以色列正在评估加沙是否有至少 20 名人质被杀，以及 32 人确诊死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 03:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-live/israel-reviewing-hamas-response-to-hostage-proposal-idf-officer-killed-in-gaza/0000018d-8196-d6dc-ab9f-cfff8a840000</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院未能通过共和党向以色列提供 170 亿美元独立援助的努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-fails-to-pass-gop-effort-to-provide-israel-with-17b-in-standalone-aid/0000018d-80c6-d6dc-ab9f-cfffec3b0000</link><description>鉴于参议院民主党人坚持将以色列援助纳入拜登总统的国家安全补充援助计划（其中包括超过 140 亿美元的以色列援助），该法案获得推进的机会为零</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 23:58:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-fails-to-pass-gop-effort-to-provide-israel-with-17b-in-standalone-aid/0000018d-80c6-d6dc-ab9f-cfffec3b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心冒犯宗教预备役军人，以色列国防军取消了女性表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/idf-cancels-womens-performance-for-fear-of-offending-religious-reservists/0000018d-8059-daa1-a9fd-e25b6ce40000</link><description>驻扎在北部的该营的士兵们请求举办一场退役派对，其中包括爱情旅的表演，但最终却得到了右翼演讲者和一名恐同拉比的一系列讲座。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 23:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/idf-cancels-womens-performance-for-fear-of-offending-religious-reservists/0000018d-8059-daa1-a9fd-e25b6ce40000</guid></item><item><title>美国对极端主义定居者的制裁使以色列极右翼财政部长陷入困境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sanctions-on-extremist-settlers-put-israels-far-right-finance-minister-in-a-bind/0000018d-801b-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f01d60000</link><description>以色列国民银行冻结了四名涉嫌暴力定居者之一的账户后，财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇誓言要采取行动，但他所能做的就是试图说服美国当局，因为他在美国不受欢迎</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 23:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sanctions-on-extremist-settlers-put-israels-far-right-finance-minister-in-a-bind/0000018d-801b-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f01d60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列寻求切断加沙对近东救济工程处的依赖，但尚不清楚谁可以取代它</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-seeks-to-sever-gazas-dependency-on-unrwa-but-its-unclear-who-could-replace-it/0000018d-8059-d636-adef-ceff82270000</link><description>这一想法是试图切断哈马斯与进入加沙地带的人道主义援助的联系的一部分。但消息人士称，潜在的替代者世界粮食计划署在加沙缺乏必要的基础设施来代替该机构的活动</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 22:21:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-seeks-to-sever-gazas-dependency-on-unrwa-but-its-unclear-who-could-replace-it/0000018d-8059-d636-adef-ceff82270000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列问题上，拜登继续选择胡萝卜而不是大棒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/biden-keeps-on-choosing-the-carrot-over-stick-when-it-comes-to-israel/0000018d-7f91-d636-adef-7fffb8290000</link><description>对于那些希望拜登最终利用军事援助作为筹码的人来说，参议院的一揽子计划还有很多不足之处</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 21:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/biden-keeps-on-choosing-the-carrot-over-stick-when-it-comes-to-israel/0000018d-7f91-d636-adef-7fffb8290000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名在加沙地带北部战斗中丧生的以色列军官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-officer-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018d-8016-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f95a20000</link><description>大卫·沙库里少校是陆军第401装甲旅作战工程兵第601营副营长。他的朋友这样评价他：“一位举止冷静的指挥官，树立了榜样”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 21:03:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-officer-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018d-8016-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f95a20000</guid></item><item><title>海法市迫于压力阻止有关以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的新书发行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-thwarts-book-launch-on-israeli-palestinian-conflict-amid-pressure/0000018d-7fa2-daa1-a9fd-7faa3d1c0000</link><description>在市内政党的压力下，市政府宣布“推迟活动”，但没有确定新的日期。民权协会猛烈抨击此举，而右翼分子则赞扬此举</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 20:40:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-thwarts-book-launch-on-israeli-palestinian-conflict-amid-pressure/0000018d-7fa2-daa1-a9fd-7faa3d1c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>